metadata.name: Bullish Circuit Sentimentality : Gold Genesis
metadata.description:
My first experimental work and skill development exercise using Affinity Designer to create this style and technique.

The original colours I started out with was Gold on blue, but obviously staring at this for a long time was not sustainable. So now you have the black and white vectors I make.

However I do still enjoy having them in colour. They have a different life to them.

Bullish Circuit Sentimentality : Gold Genesis  
Art by TERRYLKNOX

4169 × 5905 px
